<p>Tim Ferriss&#8217; new book <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/030746363X/zenhab-20/ref=nosim/">The 4-Hour Body</a> is now out and I&#8217;ve been reading it for a week now. It&#8217;s utterly fascinating.</p>
<p>Tim as you know is the author of <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0307465357/zenhab-20/ref=nosim/">The 4-Hour Workweek</a>, a huge best-selling book, and his new book looks to be just as successful.</p>
