		<title>Get Inspired</title>
		<link>http://zenhabits.net/get-inspired/</link>
		<comments>http://zenhabits.net/get-inspired/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 05 Dec 2010 16:05:24 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator>Leo</dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Happiness]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://zenhabits.net/?p=7287</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[&#8216;You owe it to us all to get on with what you&#8217;re good at.&#8217; ~W. H. Auden
Post written by Leo Babauta.
